<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ask-v">ask <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɑːsk/    美 /æsk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>问；询问：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She asked Mary what time it was. 
她问玛丽几点了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ll have to ask someone the way to the station. 
我们得去问一下车站怎么走。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>asked about</strong> Jesse’s health. 
她询问了杰西的健康状况。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>要求；请求：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>ask (sb) to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One evening, a passer-by asked to stay for the night.
一天晚上，有个过路人请求借宿一晚。</p><footer>2008 陕西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People may feel forced when asked to do things that they don’t want to.
当被要求做自己不愿做的事情时，人们会有种被迫的感觉。</p><footer>2016 江苏书面表达</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>ask + that / wh- 从句:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She asked that she should be kept informed of developments. 
她要求向她报告进展情况。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>ask (sb) for sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t be afraid of asking (others) for help when it is needed.
需要时不要害怕(向他人)求助。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I went into a cafe and asked for a coffee. 
我走进一家咖啡馆要了杯咖啡。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>邀请：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>ask sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She’s asked him to come to the party. 
她已邀请他来参加聚会。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>索要 (价格)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s <strong>asking</strong> ￡80 a month rent <strong>for</strong> that flat. 
那套公寓月租他要价80英镑。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="ask-for-trouble">ask for trouble</h3>
<p>1.<strong>自找麻烦；自讨苦吃</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>No matter how many times I asked to watching cartoons, my parents would not to let me. (改错)  （2018 全国）  </li>
<li>I wasn’t able to hide my eagerness when I <strong><em>_</em></strong> (ask), “What do you wish me to do now?”  （2015 湖南改）  </li>
<li>Before building a house, you will have to ask <strong><em>_</em></strong> the government’s permission.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. watching → watch; 去掉let前的to  2. asked  3. for  </p></div>